      <div class="author-bio">
        <h3>About Success Odyssey</h3>
        <p>Success Odyssey explores the ideas, philosophies, and mental models of the world's greatest thinkers — translating timeless wisdom into practical guidance for modern life and work.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="related-articles">
        <h2>Related Articles</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/blog/elon-musk-thinking">How Elon Musk Thinks: First Principles and the Physics Approach</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/naval-ravikant-wealth">Naval Ravikant's Guide to Wealth: Specific Knowledge and Leverage</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/long-term-thinking">Long-Term Thinking: The Ultimate Competitive Advantage</a></li>
